Description.Name: Flak AC/2 Ammo
Description.Details:
Ammo Bins contain the rounds needed for projectile-based weaponry, with at least one bin required per weapon type. Ammo Bins will explode and destroy their installed location when they receive a Critical Hit.

Flak rounds are anti-aircraft rounds that use proximity charges to detonate in midair. While effective against fast-moving targets, the fragments generated are too small to inflict significant damage on other combat units. Flak AC/2 Ammo Bins each contain 25 rounds and can only be used in standard and light autocannons.
